Package project.elearnt

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CorrectLinkScene
    Class for correct scenes with bad exits creates
    Exits
    This class responsible for represented the obtain image (whether for take picture or select from gallery), and then draw the selection area for create an exit
    Finish
    Class for established a connection with server, and then send files to him
    ImageAdapter
    Class to adapt images in the gallery
    LinkSceneNode
    This class represent a scene exit
    ListLinkScene
    This class create and modify the list of scene exits
    ListScene
    Class to create and modify a scene list, furthermore create xml files
    Main
    This is the principal class of the app (Main Activity), so, contains the Launcher and the option to create a project and exit from it.
    MakeExits
    This class responsible for get the principal properties of the link scene name (name and text)
    ProjectExists
    This class responsible for correct the before projects creates between the options figures create again, modify (name and graphic mode), delete and send
    Properties
    This class responsible for make the principal options of the project, like, name and graphic mode, when finish, if project not exists create then in the directory specified by path_projects, else start activity ProjectExists to modify (recreate, change, delete or send)
    SceneNode
    This class represent a scene
    Scenes
    This class responsible for create new scenes or correct the before scenes creates between the options figures modify, delete and correct link scenes name
    ScenesGallery
    Class to represent a custom gallery with images in project
